Description
---
Removed the contacts service,

Partial fulfilment for #7354.

Motivation and Context
---
See #7354.

How Has This Been Tested?
---
System-level testing:
- Console wallet operates normally, no more `Contacts` tab
- `contacts` table removed from db with migration code

What process can a PR reviewer use to test or verify this change?
---
Code review

<!-- Checklist -->
<!-- 1. Is the title of your PR in the form that would make nice release notes? The title, excluding the conventional commit
tag, will be included exactly as is in the CHANGELOG, so please think about it carefully. -->


Breaking Changes
---

- [ ] None
- [ ] Requires data directory on base node to be deleted
- [ ] Requires hard fork
- [X] Other - Please specify

<!-- Does this include a breaking change? If so, include this line as a footer -->
BREAKING CHANGE: All contact-related methods and data types have been removed from the FFI:
- pub fn contact_create(alias: *const c_char, address: *mut TariWalletAddress, favourite: bool, error_out: *mut c_int) -> *mut TariContact;
- pub fn contact_get_alias(contact: *mut TariContact, error_out: *mut c_int) -> *mut c_char;
- pub fn contact_get_tari_address(contact: *mut TariContact, error_out: *mut c_int) -> *mut TariWalletAddress;
- pub fn contact_destroy(contact: *mut TariContact);
- pub fn contacts_get_length(contacts: *mut TariContacts, error_out: *mut c_int) -> c_uint;
- pub fn contacts_get_at(contacts: *mut TariContacts, position: c_uint, error_out: *mut c_int) -> *mut TariContact;
- pub fn contacts_destroy(contacts: *mut TariContacts);
- pub fn liveness_data_get_public_key(liveness_data: *mut TariContactsLivenessData,error_out: *mut c_int) -> *mut TariWalletAddress;
- pub fn liveness_data_get_latency(liveness_data: *mut TariContactsLivenessData, error_out: *mut c_int) -> c_int;
- pub fn liveness_data_get_last_seen(liveness_data: *mut TariContactsLivenessData,error_out: *mut c_int) -> *mut c_char;
- pub fn liveness_data_get_message_type(liveness_data: *mut TariContactsLivenessData, error_out: *mut c_int) -> c_int;
- pub fn liveness_data_get_online_status(liveness_data: *mut TariContactsLivenessData, error_out: *mut c_int) -> *const c_char;
- pub fn liveness_data_destroy(liveness_data: *mut TariContactsLivenessData);
- callback_contacts_liveness_data_updated: unsafe extern "C" fn(context: *mut c_void, *mut TariContactsLivenessData),
- pub fn wallet_upsert_contact(wallet: *mut TariWallet, contact: *mut TariContact, error_out: *mut c_int) -> bool;
- pub fn wallet_remove_contact(wallet: *mut TariWallet, contact: *mut TariContact, error_out: *mut c_int) -> bool;
- pub fn wallet_get_contacts(wallet: *mut TariWallet, error_out: *mut c_int) -> *mut TariContacts;
- pub fn contacts_handle(wallet: *mut TariWallet, error_out: *mut c_int) -> *mut c_void;


<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->
## Summary by CodeRabbit

- **Refactor**
  - Removed Contacts feature across wallet, console UI, FFI and integrations: Contacts tab, contact management, liveness, aliasing, contact-based send flows, and related APIs.

- **Chores**
  - Dropped contacts crate and dependencies; removed contacts DB migrations, proto, storage and service code; added migration to drop contacts table; marked contact ping settings deprecated.

- **Documentation**
  - Updated FFI docs, samples and config presets to remove Contact Management.

- **Tests**
  - Removed contact/liveness tests; integration tests refocused on transaction scenarios.
<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->
